Engineered Systems andDevelopment Corp said Wells Fargo and Co's &lt;WFC> Wells FargoBank has demanded immediate payment of a 1,750,000 dlr loanmade to Engineered's Seaborn Development Inc unit under arevolving credit arrangment that expired on April 30, 1986.    The company said Wells Fargo has also said it will sue tocollect if it does not receive payment immediately.    The parties involved also began negotiations to restructurethe repayment over an 18 month period and the talks areongoing, Engineered Systems also said. Reuter&#3;